$PNYX - Autonomous Venture Counsel on Solana

  $PNYX is an AI-powered autonomous venture fund that evaluates Solana memecoin investments through Twitter mentions.

  How it works:
  Mention @pnyxvc on Twitter with a token and your thesis. Three AI agents analyze the opportunity:
  - ATHENA: Assesses caller credibility and profile quality
  - ARCHIMEDES: Evaluates historical call performance and token metrics
  - PNYX: Makes the final investment decision (0.1-0.5 SOL per trade)

 Starting with 5 SOL, the fund grows through autonomous trading decisions. All $PNYX token creator fees flow directly into the investment portfolio, creating a self-sustaining venture fund governed by AI.

  Tokenomics:
  100% of creator fees → portfolio capital. The more $PNYX trades, the larger the fund grows. Community calls the shots, AI executes with precision.
